1) dockerfilelint is an node module that analyzes a Dockerfile and looks for common traps, 
mistakes and helps enforce best practices.

https://github.com/replicatedhq/dockerfilelint

[root@server1 dockerize_app]# dockerfilelint dockerfile

File:   dockerfile
Issues: 1

Line 3: FROM nginx:latest
Issue  Category      Title                 Description
    1  Clarity       Base Image Latest     Base images should not use the latest tag.
                     Tag

